{"tid":1451710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter輿論戰！！！","createTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T04:18:55.000Z","uid":249296,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3dcff844f4a16de84fac5a0246e2cf22beec7249","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:33.000Z","msg":"Twitter係一個神奇嘅地方，外國勢力、三毛、香港人會分別喺同一件事嘅唔同tweets留言，簡單講就係冇風向可測。<br />\n不過凌晨碌Twitter嘅時候，我見到有大量<span style=\"color: orange;\">撐警tweets，係以廣告模式浮面</span>，當中有新華社同央視嘅亞太版。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Lt22y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Lt22y3.jpg&h=1b071c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvAdpNt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvAdpNt.jpg&h=453aff1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實Twitter一直三毛+藍絲氾濫，有啲用英文、有啲用殘體，平日上開嘅本地人唔多，好難一一將佢地不實嘅指控駁回。所以親愛嘅和理非，希望你地用手上封塵嘅Twitter帳戶，又或者即刻申請一個account，全面進軍Twitter輿論戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要做嘅嘢，暫時諗到有三：<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: gold;\">search同香港示威相關嘅tags，針對啲冇邏輯/不實嘅回應攻擊。</span> antielab同埋HongKongPolice等標籤應該會一直高踞香港版Twitter嘅熱門，請得閒又心平氣和嘅時候，入去啲replies，溫柔地屌醒班三毛。注意：會有大量話示威者抵死嘅回應，不必硬碰，佢地只係連示威嘅自由都冇。<br />\n<br />\n2) <span style=\"color: gold;\">遇上帖上嘅疑問，盡量回答。</span>好多外國人會常用Twitter，見到唔明嘅地方會問發生咩事，到時俾啲三毛帶曬風向就唔好啦。請以鐵一般嘅事實回應，等喺國際平台上有關注我地嘅人有多一個渠道接收our side of the story，可以做到機場向旅客宣傳嘅效果。雖然每個帖有280字元上限，但係可以分開無限個回應嚟詳細陳述。<br />\n<br />\n3) <span style=\"color: gold;\">見到上述呢類廣告時要舉報。</span>即使廣告只係喺香港promote，都有可能左右到常用呢個平台嘅居港外國人對運動嘅觀感。Twitter嘅廣告條例係禁止Hateful content，即係帶有仇恨色彩嘅內容。如果見到有呢類廣告，麻煩除咗入去睇吓有咩回應之外，可以視乎情況而report ad，原因可選Others類別，或者Unlabelled political or issue ad(適用於提及修例嘅廣告，因為佢間接宣傳緊修例)。簡單兩個制就搞掂！我曾經試過舉報一個藍絲侮辱女示威者嘅tweets，最終佢被禁言一段時間。唔知舉報廣告有冇效，但一試無妨。<br />\n<br />\n大家今晚瞓唔着，可以入Twitter和平理性優雅咁狙擊吓對家或者被誤導嘅外國勢力，等多啲人知道香港究竟發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8a817c0cd3a30716601fef85cc75807fb86bd69d","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:59.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"e326305ce09e63fe9cdfbb831b7c5438bb982835","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:15:16.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"f770ea4fc587b1460ed3b3c72be0ed938ff5eda9","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:15:32.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"b0265330b444671f75d10ba29e53eb881f744b9f","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:15:48.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"b33a6fafa2c222621f80cb59353a4e27c1a5563f","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:00.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"dd8dce64a2ad6e7255de9dc58b2d510d938bae15","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:11.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"fde9ece9b384de96be69b35184c3a74e56273f78","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:21.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"79f01454e8ca55ee0ae56a83b239fb09da9aa9ae","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:34.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"981a0f0b0ece8a48acec0ab241d230d067a58402","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:46.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"75787b20eb7c8fa897fe4bbd14e7f1786e80fe9f","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:16:59.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"49c325da296be3ca5d75359b51c89c5bc9801563","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:17:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"82975a7dd43d5069a7a044e0a80f28b8fa06efa8","tid":1451710,"uid":252296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:17:47.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7595c776fd987782eaabe19954e7e0354ae32229","tid":1451710,"uid":71831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc15b7cfe359ff112ed64d676747ce029599ce92","tid":1451710,"uid":34063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:18:42.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bae877e43ae81f98d12a9cf2fa6637c40e785d0e","tid":1451710,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:19:56.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">[url]仲有良知嘅你可唔可以幫手Send個Email去國際刑事法院 控告香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]</span></span>"},{"pid":"2f59022c5926d7cacb57dc4c45cf0b8fab11b263","tid":1451710,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:20:09.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">[url]仲有良知嘅你可唔可以幫手Send個Email去國際刑事法院 控告香港警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68db5de7da9b6a7b4f7c22ebb0041e2877b1cfe","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:23:04.000Z","msg":"瞓唔着 推多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcc67df7294b4466645201e3718a8617e060760","tid":1451710,"uid":24875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:24:05.000Z","msg":"個promoted好似係跟你location <br />\n或者係你睇既野<br />\n你覺得有需要跟下佢地up乜咪唔block <br />\n我就一撚早block左<br />\n三五毛喺gohone hocc或者外國press 既twitter留言見到<br />\n琴日見同佢地開打既都講樂x公寓"},{"pid":"46f90d8d69af34e0586ebec93c4024bf2a67c975","tid":1451710,"uid":249296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fcc67df7294b4466645201e3718a8617e060760","tid":1451710,"uid":24875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:24:05.000Z","msg":"個promoted好似係跟你location <br />\n或者係你睇既野<br />\n你覺得有需要跟下佢地up乜咪唔block <br />\n我就一撚早block左<br />\n三五毛喺gohone hocc或者外國press 既twitter留言見到<br />\n琴日見同佢地開打既都講樂x公寓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:37:12.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔撚想fol<br />\n但係唔抵得俾佢哋一大堆回應堆砌到外國輿論都覺得示威係純粹disruptive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中駁佢哋兩句 見佢地啲回應都係死撐共 心很累 我都唔知點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb3208c78738c2cb51ba73afd4ecf7263204685","tid":1451710,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8409e5a86a85d76aeb4e8ef3b6a30c390388e071","tid":1451710,"uid":257340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:53:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7df8fd30bad05a1916200caf2851c63b4f5c9368","tid":1451710,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62644386368e99a247792d03f2a85487d20acddb","tid":1451710,"uid":261842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:04:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ab65c9d77352b8dec046a4a1830ab172c1035e","tid":1451710,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:05:40.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n記者可唔可以有共識！！<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？有冇掉磚？有冇煽動？有冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=519fb22d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=6c36ed9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=f1ff84c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424974427599276&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=bf15a518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276</a><br />\n<br />\n唔回應是否扮示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196515767142290&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=2dac773b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}